<item>
            <title>[LU-14574] lfs find --mdt-count doesn&apos;t work on mountpoint or non-striped directories</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14574</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# lfs mkdir -c2 /mnt/lustre/d2
# lfs find /mnt/lustre
/mnt/lustre
/mnt/lustre/d0
/mnt/lustre/d2
# lfs find --mdt-count=2 /mnt/lustre
error: find failed for /mnt/lustre.
# lfs find --mdt-count=2 /mnt/lustre/d0
error: find failed for /mnt/lustre/d0.
# lfs find --mdt-count=2 /mnt/lustre/d2
/mnt/lustre/d2
# lfs mkdir -c2 /mnt/lustre/d0/d1
# lfs find --mdt-count=2 /mnt/lustre/d0
error: find failed for /mnt/lustre/d0.
# lfs find --mdt-count=2 /mnt/lustre/d2
/mnt/lustre/d2
# lfs find --mdt-count=2 /mnt/lustre/d0/d1
/mnt/lustre/d0/d1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
